# the seed

## Requirements

* https://github.com/metaversesystems/libecs-cpp

* Autotools

* Libtool

## Compiling

```
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure
$ make
```

## Components

To create a component, enter the ```./components``` directory:

```
$ cd components
$ ./create_component.sh component_name email@address.com
```

## Systems

To create a system, enter the ```./systems``` directory:

```
$ cd systems
$ ./create_system.sh system_name email@address.com
```
